replies.body:
@Riot

Going to point out the elephant in the room here, but not everyone who plays LoL shops at Baby Gap for their clothing. Will there ever be any sizes on clothing bigger than 2XL?

Yes, 2XL is big, but again, there are people who are bigger and wear 3XL or 4XL in this world. And that's a demographic who cannot buy Riot's clothing because they don't fit into the clothing.
